                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse225">What documents do I need to make an application?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse225" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>The documents needed varies depending on the type of application.</p>
						<br>
						<p><strong>For an individual/joint application</strong><br />
						<ul>
							<li>  - A scanned passport photograph of applicant</li>
							<li>  - Scanned original copy of the property survey plan</li>
							<li>  - Scanned Evidence of ownership (either any of family receipt/ sworn affidavit/sales agreement)</li>
							<li>  - Scanned evidence of payment of three years development levy</li>
						</ul>
						<p><strong>For corporate application</strong><br />
						<ul>
							<li>  - Scanned copy of certificate of incorporation</li>
							<li>  - Scanned copy of feasibility report (for property above 5000 hecter)</li>
							<li>  - Scanned copy of security report/ fire service report (for petrol station)</li>
						</ul>
						</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
