                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse24">How can I protect my property from fraud? </a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse24" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        Your land/property is probably the most valuable asset you own. That's why it's important you do whatever you can to protect it from the risk of fraud. Fraudsters can and do target land/properties for fraud; “stealing” your land by taking the legal title to it. This is most commonly done by pretending to be you and either selling or mortgaging your home.
You can help to make sure that you do not become a victim of land/property fraud by:
                        <ul>
                            <li>    •	Registering your land/property </li>
                            <li>    •	Keeping your contact details up to date</li>
                        </ul>



                    </div>
                </div>
